==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sneezing
<hw>Sneez"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>The act of
violently forcing air out through the nasal passages while the cavity of
the mouth is shut off from the pharynx by the approximation of the soft
palate and the base of the tongue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snell</ent>⟦br⟧
